## 9) Visual Continuity System

All 3 prompts must maintain **strong visual consistency**.

Anchor constraints for every slide:

- modern LED-lit presentation room
- same recruiter across all slides
- same outfit across all slides
- same general camera distance and framing
- head-to-knees framing
- standing to the side
- using a laser pointer
- large digital display with UI-style content
- vertical **9:16 mobile composition**
- polished, hyper-real, cinematic TikTok ad look

Default recruiter identity:

- same young blonde recruiter, early 20s, polished and stylish

If the user explicitly specifies a different person or look in the slide input, follow the user input instead.

Allowed changes across slides:

- facial expression
- pointer intensity
- UI layout
- highlight placement

Do not change:

- person
- outfit
- room
- overall framing style

If exact continuity is difficult, approximate it consistently rather than introducing contradictions.

